# Sort Wise ♻️

Sort Wise is a Deep Learning project for image classification and smart waste sorting.  

The system classifies waste images into different categories using CNNs and transfer learning models.

## Overview!
This project aims to improve waste management and recycling processes by automatically identifying waste categories from images.

The notebook includes:
- Data preprocessing
- Data exploration and visualization
- Model training
- Model evaluation
- Model comparison

## Models Used ~
The project experiments with:
- MobileNetV2
- EfficientNet
